Human Rights Watch says ISIS is guilty of war crimes against Yazidi women and girls . 
  Children as young as eight have been abducted and raped by ISIS fighters . 
  Victims were separated from their families and forced to marry and convert to Islam . 
  Human Rights Watch interviewed 20 survivors of ISIS rape and sexual assault . 
  One child said she was raped by seven different men for three days . 
  Another said she tried to kill herself to avoid being raped again . 
  Victims and children were kidnapped from their homes in northern Iraq and forced into marriage . 
  ISIS fighters were kidnapping women and children and raping them repeatedly, study says . 
  Some victims were selected from a lottery of men to rape . 
 